nodes.text: "More Starships!" is a Starships of the Galaxy web supplement that was published on Wizards of the Coast's website. It was written by Brian Campbell and Owen K.C. Stephens and published online November 15, 2001.
This supplement to Star Wars Roleplaying Game details the TIE/D Defender, the YT-1930, and the Shieldship.
